Comedian and voice compere Adeniran Oyewole aka Herbegbeyin is set for the fourth edition of his annual show tagged Herbegbeyin Undiluted 4.0 (The Thanksgiving). According to Herbigbeyin’s team, the show is set to hold on Sunday, July 17, 2022, at Terra Kulture on Victoria Island.   Depression notifies me when to switch my style – Rema     I’m inspired by Burna Boy’s tenancity – Blaqbonez     Yul Edochie calls out Ahmed Musa over post   Other acts that will be joining Herbegbeyin include Asiri, Doctor Frique, Mr. Talk, MC Rhelax, Elijah Daniel, BBQ, Prince Da Psalmist, TMO, MC Bleach, HPrince, Okandeji, Adeola Testimony, MC Dee, MC Sege, Moskey, Akanlaff, Femi Praise, and Scriptural Tungba. In a chat about the show, Herbegbeyin said the show is simply an expression of gratitude to his fans and family who have stood with him through the time and tides. “For People who have stood with me through tough times and have crossed that embargo with me. It’s a moment of gratitude, music, and of course intense laughter from me and my friends,” he said.